{"tid":1813920,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"去屯市商場要小心！！連大公司都冇基本衛生常識","createTime":"2020-01-06T15:17:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-09T11:07:34.000Z","uid":336479,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"77384f32e74c4b56977e7dc42b6409b2bddfcb11","tid":1813920,"uid":336479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T15:17:18.000Z","msg":"事源係今日去屯門市中心的商場廁所，同個當值員工吹水就發現原來信X旗下外判的恒毅環衞服務有限公司對員工連基本尊重都冇，之前都聽過外判工係出名苛刻，點知呢間仲要係濕尻。<br />\n<br />\n流感高峰期，佢地上頭竟然<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔俾員工出廁所飲水</span></span>，員工要斟水就要佢地去隔離餐廳拎水，但明明本身應該係翻自己公司寫字樓斟水，而唔係要佢地好似乞水咁....<br />\n<br />\n一間人流咁多的商場，佢的廁所外判左俾一間公司係完全<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔尊重人</span></span>之餘，衛生常識同危機意識都係零，個員工唔敢出聲，我就唯有係網上面make some noise，希望佢地可以重視翻員工的尊嚴，即使係廁所清潔工都好，佢地都有人權，都係deserve<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">尊重</span></span>，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔係你班高層就有權當人地底泥</span></span>，一間公司有冇質素，喺呢啲細節就可以見到。"},{"pid":"e8ab5d1b4f82002c1ab740175c4e1ec95fa6d1ca","tid":1813920,"uid":42751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T15:26:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d03fcde10e76d363da104910b4df407a7bc3ddca","tid":1813920,"uid":163540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T15:34:18.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n清潔工人好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61751768c387ee864e96b088fe934494fafddfb4","tid":1813920,"uid":120658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T15:36:32.000Z","msg":"職業無分貴賤阿<br />\n清潔工都係人，仲要咁辛苦"},{"pid":"8fd6f085b04ddd9590fd4292eb402b4966e52d52","tid":1813920,"uid":187012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T15:37:20.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"f08fd1f9313e19403d19a448fefc269bed4435dd","tid":1813920,"uid":273091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re